ActMuseums Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Canadian Heritage of HEATHER HOLDEN of Vancouver, British Columbia, to be a trustee of the Board of Trustees of the Canadian Museum of Nature, to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Alice McCarron, whose term has expired.
